 {'from': 'human', 'value': 'I think establishing a routine and setting clear boundaries for myself would be beneficial. Engaging in healthy activities like exercise, pursuing hobbies, and practicing relaxation techniques could provide healthier outlets for my emotions. I also want to educate myself about addiction and learn more about the recovery process.'}
 {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "Those are excellent strategies, Charlie. By incorporating structure and self-care into your daily life, you're creating a solid foundation for your recovery journey. Remember to be patient with yourself, as healing takes time. Is there anything else you'd like to discuss or questions you have?"}
 {'from': 'human', 'value': 'Thank you, Alex. Your guidance and support mean a lot to me. I do have one more question - how can I navigate potential setbacks along the way without giving up on my progress?'}
