 {'from': 'human', 'value': 'Definitely, Alex. So, last week, we had a gathering at my place, and things got heated between two of my closest friends. It started with a small disagreement about politics, but it quickly escalated into a larger argument that seemed to touch upon deeper issues. I was taken aback by the intensity of their emotions, and it made me question the foundation of our friendship.'}
